org.wikipedia.miner.model
Class Redirect

java.lang.Object
  org.wikipedia.miner.model.Page
      org.wikipedia.miner.model.Redirect
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class Redirect
extends Page

This class represents redirects in Wikipedia; the links that have been defined to connect synonyms to the correct article (i.e Farming redirects to Agriculture). It is intended to contain all properties and methods that are relevant for a redirect.

Author:
David Milne

Redirect

public Redirect(WikipediaDatabase database,
                int id,
                java.lang.String title)
Initialises a newly created Redirect so that it represents the page given by id and title. This is the most efficient constructor as no database lookup is required.

Parameters:
database - an active WikipediaDatabase
id - the unique identifier of the redirect
title - the (case dependent) title of the redirect
